10_9	0.2608695652173913	Every year brings its own grab bag of such anomalies, but this year many of them could be linked to a phenomenon in the empty expanses of the equatorial Pacific _ a change in the ocean currents and winds that began in the early months of 1997 and that altered weather patterns around the world.
10_10	3.142857142857143	The change in the weather was, of course, the work of El Nino.
